biotools.summary: Visual extraction conversion program that provides biomedical researches with minimal computer programming background a way to generate data extraction and conversion programs. It provides a convenient graphical user interface that allows using common point and click methods to extract and arrange data in the way that is useful to their purposes and then provides the computer program to generate such results on other documents with the same formatting.
